data.description: Live simply, in the country! Home is hardy plank exterior on pier & beam. Large open living area with wood stove featuring exposed wood beams. Gleaming tin tiles for kitchen backsplash. Other elements are unique storm cellar, "Full" RV hook-ups, shop with water & electric. Beautifully wooded, fenced tract to enjoy from your full front porch or back porch. Animals allowed & NO HOA. Located off FM 3432 for quick access to Loop 1604 & SA - La Vernia ISD. THIS IS AN "AS IS" SALE. Cash Only Deal.
